WEBVTT

00:03:29.549 --> 00:03:31.773
Lakini ni kazi ya ndani,

00:03:31.797 --> 00:03:34.615
na hatuwezi kupanga amani
au uboreshaji wa kudumu

00:03:34.639 --> 00:03:37.027
kwa ajili ya watu tunaowapenda duniani.

00:03:37.051 --> 00:03:39.131
Wanapaswa kutafuta njia yao wenyewe,

00:03:39.155 --> 00:03:40.777
majibu wenyewe.

00:03:40.801 --> 00:03:44.428
Huwezi kuenda pamoja na
watoto wako wakubwa

00:03:44.452 --> 00:03:49.038
kwenye safari yao ya kishujaa.

00:03:49.062 --> 00:03:51.179
Unapaswa kuwaacha huru.

00:03:51.203 --> 00:03:53.598
Sio heshima kuwavunga.

00:03:55.088 --> 00:03:56.947
Na kama ni tatizo la mtu mwingine,

00:03:56.971 --> 00:03:59.271
labda hata wewe hauna jibu, pia.

00:03:59.295 --> 00:04:00.487
(Vicheko)